title: Filigree Work

description: Oblong, curved sides and lid, structure of lacy, silver filigree work, featuring a central, vertical, rectangular area with a single, long-stemmed flower and leaves, identical on front and reverse. Lid, upper third of box, hinged on side, small knob-like thumb catch opposite. Small oval striker on bottom.
